title: Canon EOS Utility 2.5.1.1 by hk-47
description:
NOTE:
----

This is a fixed version of the previous torrent with the same name which I uploaded. If you have downloaded it and you couldn't install the application you can either:

1. Download this one which corrects the setup error

or:

2. Manually extract setup files from the old torrent using WinRAR, navigate into Canon EOS Utility 2.5.1.1\INSTALL\COMMON folder, and run Install.exe

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is freely downloadable update from Canon website converted to a stand-alone install so it doesn't require the original Canon CD.

Download this if you:

- Lost or misplaced your CD
- Damaged your CD and it became unreadable
- Bought used Canon EOS camera and haven't got a CD with it

It supports most of the Canon EOS DSLR cameras.

More information:
hxxp://software.canon-europe.com/software/0030936.asp

Please help seeding when you are done!
